Definition: a rare but serious syndrome of childhood characterized by withdrawal and lack of social responsiveness or interest in others and serious linguistic deficits
Example: there is considerable dispute among specialists concerning infantile autism
Synonyms: autism, a, rare, but, serious, syndrome, of, childhood, characterized, by, withdrawal, and, lack, social, responsiveness, or, interest, in, others, linguistic, deficits, there, is, considerable, dispute, among, specialists, concerning, infantile
Category: noun.cognition
